column1: Now when I tested it. But that doesn't even mean that it's containing a virus. I Have no problem with it anyway and antivirus can just react on the program itself and not a virus.
Only a couple of teams have worked on a ""fix"" for AnyDVD: CRUDE (CRD), Black Riders (BRD), RESURRECTiON (by rESin), Dr.Pc Putte and a couple of others.
And the text in the NFO is clearly from the BRD release.
Basically, don't download this fake crap.
